FWIW, cert-dir let's you specify where the certificates that you want to use live and --creds let's you put  in the username/password to use for authentication.  

`docker build` doesn't have these options, but neither does 'docker pull/push' while the Buildah equivalents do.  So I think I'll see if I can add these too, but may run into issues making it happen.  The processing for the bud code is a little funkier than the from/push code in Buildah.  

@nalind @rhatdat holler if I shouldn't try adding --creds and --cert-dir to buildah/podman bud/build.
